sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Student as Обучающийся
    participant Moodle as Moodle (PEP)
    participant Observer as Event Observer Plugin (PHP)
    participant API as PDP API (FastAPI)
    participant Progress as ProgressService
    participant Reasoner as ReasoningOrchestrator
    participant Cache as Redis

    Note over Student,Moodle: Студент завершает activity в Moodle
    Student->>Moodle: завершить module/quiz/assignment
    Moodle-->>Moodle: обновить course_modules_completion / quiz_attempts

    Note over Moodle,Observer: Custom plugin ловит событие Moodle
    Moodle->>Observer: \core\event\course_module_completion_updated
    Note right of Observer: или \mod_quiz\event\attempt_submitted

    Observer->>API: POST /api/v1/events/progress
    Note right of Observer: payload: {student_id, element_id,<br/>status: completed|viewed,<br/>grade?: float, timestamp}

    API->>Progress: record_progress_event(payload)
    Progress->>Progress: ProgressRepository.upsert_record
    Progress->>Reasoner: invalidate_and_rebuild(student_id)

    Reasoner->>Cache: DEL access:{student_id}:*
    Note right of Reasoner: lazy rebuild на следующий cache-miss<br/>(см. алгоритм А5)

    Reasoner-->>Progress: ReasoningResult
    Progress-->>API: {ok: true, ontology_version}
    API-->>Observer: 200 OK

    Note over Observer,Moodle: На следующем render Moodle вызовет<br/>availability check (см. вторую sequence-диаграмму)
